ZH: 这个国家的经济一直保持着稳定的贸易顺差。
EN: This country's economy has maintained a stable trade surplus.

ZH: 去年我国的对外贸易产生了巨额的顺差。
EN: Last year, our country had a huge trade surplus in foreign trade.

ZH: 这个行业在外贸方面一直有着明显的顺差。
EN: This industry has always had a noticeable trade surplus in foreign trade.

ZH: 近年来，我国的贸易顺差一直在增加。
EN: In recent years, our country's trade surplus has been increasing.

ZH: 他们的公司一直在努力保持着正面的贸易顺差。
EN: Their company has been working hard to maintain a positive trade surplus.

ZH: 这个国家的贸易顺差直逼了十亿美元。
EN: The trade surplus of this country is close to one billion US dollars.

ZH: 这个行业的贸易顺差对整个国家的经济起着重要作用。
EN: The trade surplus of this industry plays an important role in the country's economy.

ZH: 他们公司的产品一直在海外市场保持着顺差。
EN: Their company's products have always maintained a surplus in overseas markets.

ZH: 最近的统计数字显示，我们的贸易顺差在逐渐增加。
EN: Recent statistics show that our trade surplus is gradually increasing.

ZH: 有些专家担心贸易顺差的增加可能会导致通货膨胀。
EN: Some experts are concerned that the increase in trade surplus may lead to inflation.

ZH: 这个地区一直以来处于贸易顺差的状态。
EN: This region has always been in a trade surplus state.

ZH: 我们希望能够继续保持着贸易顺差的势头。
EN: We hope to continue the momentum of maintaining a trade surplus.

ZH: 近期，全球范围内的贸易顺差有所下降。
EN: Recently, the trade surplus on a global scale has decreased.

ZH: 这个国家的贸易顺差超过了其他国家。
EN: The trade surplus of this country exceeds that of others.

ZH: 贸易顺差可以帮助国家增加外汇储备。
EN: Trade surplus can help a country increase its foreign exchange reserves.

ZH: 年度贸易顺差已超出了预期。
EN: The annual trade surplus has exceeded expectations.

ZH: 贸易顺差的增加有助于提高国家的国际竞争力。
EN: The increase in trade surplus helps to enhance the country's international competitiveness.

ZH: 政府正在努力通过贸易顺差来吸引更多外商投资。
EN: The government is trying to attract more foreign investment through trade surplus.

ZH: 去年公司的贸易顺差创记录地增长了。
EN: The company's trade surplus grew to record levels last year.

ZH: 这次贸易协议会对顺差带来积极的影响。
EN: This trade agreement will have a positive impact on the trade surplus.
